### ğŸ” KQL Query Used (Option B)
```kql
DeviceFileEvents
| where TimeGenerated between (datetime(2025-12-01) .. datetime(2026-01-01))
| where DeviceName == "main1-srvr"
| where isnotempty(InitiatingProcessRemoteSessionDeviceName)
| summarize FirstSeen=min(TimeGenerated), LastSeen=max(TimeGenerated), Hits=count()
    by InitiatingProcessRemoteSessionDeviceName, InitiatingProcessRemoteSessionIP
| order by Hits desc
